{"tid":146801,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"12日京板奈神之旅 求指點","createTime":"2017-03-07T11:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T07:56:11.000Z","uid":89723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24493f224dbf999fcbcde3a4a625d35783c39264","tid":146801,"uid":89723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"小弟同女朋友下星期會去大阪 京都 奈良 神戶玩<br />\n未去過無經歷，行程如下，求指點<br />\n<br />\n第一日：晚機到直去京都airbnb （住東福寺個邊）食野訓<br />\n<br />\n第二日：伏見稻荷-》宇治，宇治上神社，宇治神社（半日遊）-》6點去到東山花燈路<br />\n<br />\n第三日：金閣寺-》JR馬堀站行去龜岡站坐嵐山小火車-》竹林大道-》野宮神社-》天龍寺-》渡月橋-》嵐山公園-》京都車站（食晚餐加睇京都塔）<br />\n<br />\n第四日：早上去清水寺租和服-》清水寺-》地主神社-》二年坂三年坂-》八坂神社，祇園-》還衫-》錦市場-》河原町鴨川（晚餐散步）<br />\n<br />\n第五日：Airbnb checkout -》河原町坐去阪急梅田-》食野行下等3點check in (住堺筋本町附近)-》未諗去邊，晚餐應該食大起水產<br />\n<br />\n第六日：神戶一日遊-》食lunch-》生田神社-》垂水三井outlet-》神戶港睇夜景-》返大阪<br />\n<br />\n第七日：奈良玩鹿-》東大寺-》諗唔到去邊-》晚上想食心齋橋吉列牛<br />\n<br />\n第八日：黑門-》日本橋-》心齋橋-》美國村-》道頓堀-》力丸燒肉<br />\n<br />\n第九日：天守閣+大阪城公園-》四天王寺-》通天閣-》磯丸水產-》晚上梅田空中庭園展望台睇景-》hep five摩天輪 （大阪周遊卡）<br />\n<br />\n第十日：唔知去邊<br />\n<br />\n第十一日：已經唔知去邊<br />\n<br />\n第十二日：關西空港outlet-》返香港<br />\n<br />\n有無建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08085055fad43b3175065bf777775ac8dab10f68","tid":146801,"uid":2321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"伏見稻荷有山行，你預3個鐘到玩晒（包埋影相時間）<br />\n行完會攰，放d hea既係後面"},{"pid":"b87740974264d02506cc80ad38a6b6b327c8fe4b","tid":146801,"uid":2321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"難波心斎橋可以行1日或以上"},{"pid":"94497876552878d9c80f13812ebc67e69d064f7d","tid":146801,"uid":89723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求指點"},{"pid":"6736f6f25b3c3ed39a20901b8c8708da7f1b1306","tid":146801,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"姫路城+明石海峽大橋<br />\n近江八幡堀+彦根城<br />\n二条城+太秦博物館<br />\n貴船神社+鞍馬<br />\n甲賀或伊賀忍者村<br />\n平安神宮 <br />\n三十三間堂 <br />\n東寺<br />\n舞鶴吉原 天橋立 <br />\nJR鐵路博物館<br />\n京都御所"},{"pid":"2aa1c607a84ce86ec5cf1f3afd413f14db42ade7","tid":146801,"uid":2480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"神戶個三井outlet我上次行左大半日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚你地唔夠時間去下一站"},{"pid":"5ee2971c9c2b87710f602b8e222473930457edbd","tid":146801,"uid":89723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神戶個三井outlet我上次行左大半日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚你地唔夠時間去下一站</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三井outlet行4個鐘夠唔夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨走個日都會去關西空港個outlet"},{"pid":"9f360694effbd997045fd1235d1020c761ecd0d4","tid":146801,"uid":2480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T00:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>神戶個三井outlet我上次行左大半日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚你地唔夠時間去下一站</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三井outlet行4個鐘夠唔夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨走個日都會去關西空港個outlet</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搞錯左三田果個premium outlet, 因為都係神戶附近<br />\n<br />\n4個鐘夠唔夠行就睇你女友有幾強購買力啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba66bb7b8a8af0034e7e83ff51e7c4d06bf9cdfe","tid":146801,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:33:02.000Z","msg":"唔去姬路城睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d823b47211838c02bc7908bbe7a9fca27ab1da21","tid":146801,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伏見稻荷有山行，你預3個鐘到玩晒（包埋影相時間）<br />\n行完會攰，放d hea既係後面</blockquote><br />\n路過，我想問伏見係咪朝早去最好，因為第一日到京都9點半機，過到京都check in 埋應該下晝2,3點，諗緊個日行程去唔去伏見好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958cf6040cdf8ad65d2079934842b8bf517cf4a1","tid":146801,"uid":77317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>伏見稻荷有山行，你預3個鐘到玩晒（包埋影相時間）<br />\n行完會攰，放d hea既係後面</blockquote><br />\n路過，我想問伏見係咪朝早去最好，因為第一日到京都9點半機，過到京都check in 埋應該下晝2,3點，諗緊個日行程去唔去伏見好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果次去無上晒山(上到千本鳥居落返黎)大約個半鐘~~你可以諗諗"},{"pid":"251c6350bf946a79863819e881735a7d016d951c","tid":146801,"uid":77317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"就咁睇幾個問題<br />\n1) 東山花燈路今年係3月3到3月12...<br />\n所以你下星期去應該睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"http://www.hanatouro.jp/higashiyama/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hanatouro.jp%2Fhigashiyama%2Findex.html&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=29d0ea29\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hanatouro.jp/higashiyama/index.html</a><br />\n IF到時真係有既,東山花燈路其實包清水寺果頭,你再睇睇<br />\n2)奈良玩鹿可以包埋春日大社...果度應該夠你玩大半日<br />\n<br />\n3)後面兩日可以有好多玩法,樓上都有人講<br />\n如有興趣可以買JR 關西PASS(名自己再查下)<br />\n坐新幹線可以去姬路城,再唔係去埋岡山倉敷仲得<br />\n要睇你地想睇城定睇景定其他<br />\n<br />\n<strong>姫路城+明石海峽大橋</strong><br />\n近江八幡堀+<strong>彦根城</strong><br />\n<strong>二条城</strong>+太秦博物館<br />\n<strong>貴船神社</strong>+鞍馬<br />\n甲賀或伊賀忍者村<br />\n平安神宮 <br />\n三十三間堂 <br />\n東寺<br />\n舞鶴吉原<strong> 天橋立 </strong><br />\nJR鐵路博物館<br />\n京都御所<br />\n<br />\n粗字我有去過,可以問我~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf14f074b43d350446427f88acb37f626ad70bcf","tid":146801,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>伏見稻荷有山行，你預3個鐘到玩晒（包埋影相時間）<br />\n行完會攰，放d hea既係後面</blockquote><br />\n路過，我想問伏見係咪朝早去最好，因為第一日到京都9點半機，過到京都check in 埋應該下晝2,3點，諗緊個日行程去唔去伏見好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果次去無上晒山(上到千本鳥居落返黎)大約個半鐘~~你可以諗諗</blockquote><br />\n照你咁講，我都係第二日去好d,咁樣都應該玩到半日，雖然我一個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}